{"tid":1059272,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點先可以正常落到巴士","createTime":"2019-03-13T04:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T04:45:31.000Z","uid":237084,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"22ce72f085a5d9af35dfc1739d4aca1fbaf46e24","tid":1059272,"uid":237084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:30:28.000Z","msg":"每次見到佢都無次正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次我好近個站先㩒鐘，見到佢上客之後都無開門就望一望司機位想開聲之際<br />\n佢就問係咪有落啊 我話係佢就開門<br />\n第二次有另一個女人一早㩒咗鐘企喺門邊等 <br />\n佢望個站無客就一嘢扭駄想走<br />\n個女人狂叫有落啊 㩒咗鐘㗎！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個司機就望一望呆一呆先開門<br />\n經過兩次我就認得依個戴住副超嘅司機<br />\n最近一次見到佢 我都已經好有戒心<br />\n㩒咗鐘都隨時準備開聲叫有落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知好衰唔衰 佢停咗係外線<br />\n因為入面條線有一前一後嘅車頂住<br />\n站係無人嘅 我見佢停咁耐以為佢想前面架車走咗再埋線放我啦<br />\n點知佢見前面架車一開就跟住比油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我岀聲司機有落啊嗰時已經無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢今次仲要望都無望過嚟<br />\n好似睇唔到又聽唔到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有咩方法下次又上咗佢車可以普普通通落到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c311f249f015e2ceca953d446c40c0c211651f86","tid":1059272,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:33:29.000Z","msg":"開名啦 老奉唔睇鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0a53785a689af25db0da73d4fc3a6e00162cc2","tid":1059272,"uid":1550,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T04:35:55.000Z","msg":"打去投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2482242a63f03980ba5ef9e28a766660e048c536","tid":1059272,"uid":237084,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c311f249